# Bash Command Rules

**NEVER use `&&` or `;` to chain commands.** Each command must be on its own line due to Windows PowerShell compatibility.

❌ `cd backend && npm install`  
✅ `cd backend` then `npm install`

Exception: Pipes (`|`) are allowed as they're a single command.
